{"type":"text","timestamp":1775849850442,"sessionID":"ses_2871baca0ffejE15ebsxkZPstG","part":{"id":"prt_d78e63560001BOqcM7oRhfWPs8","messageID":"msg_d78e5ebfa001Kp2GFx9uYMjRVe","sessionID":"ses_2871baca0ffejE15ebsxkZPstG","type":"text","text":"I've successfully added the AR-010 proposal for Router Session Management to the proposal.md file. The proposal covers:\n\n- **Purpose**: Session management for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter invocations\n- **Scope**: Session creation, retrieval via Redis caching, lifecycle management, WorkloadManager integration\n- **Design Decisions**: Redis storage, Cache-Aside pattern, UUID v4 session IDs, strict input validation\n- **Alternatives**: Compared memory storage, no caching, database storage, and client-generated IDs\n- **Implementation**: 8-day plan across 7 phases from core interfaces to testing and documentation\n- **Testing**: Unit, integration, and performance tests with specific success criteria (>99% creation rate, >90% cache hit, <10ms P99 latency)","time":{"start":1775849850440,"end":1775849850440}}}
